0I%20wore%20each%20shoe%20on%20three%20or%20more%20walks.%20Some%20shoes%20proved%20to%20be%20too%20stiff%2C%20not%20supportive%20enough%2C%20or%20otherwise%20uncomfortable%20after%20just%20a%20quarter%20mile%20and%20were%20immediately%20put%20in%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20category.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20sandals%20and%20sneakers%20that%20made%20it%20through%20the%20initial%20assessment%2C%20I%20walked%20in%20each%20pair%20for%20at%20least%202%20miles%2C%20both%20outdoors%20on%20pavement%20and%20indoor%20on%20a%20treadmill%20or%20my%20walking%20desk%2C%20and%20continued%20to%20wear%20them%20for%20an%20entire%20day%20around%20the%20house%20and%20running%20errands%20to%20determine%20how%20breathable%2C%20stiff%2C%20and%20cushioned%20they%20feel%20after%20multiple%20hours%20of%20wear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20the%20final%20selections%20have%20proven%20that%20they%20are%20comfortable%20not%20only%20for%20walking%20multiple%20miles%2C%20but%20also%20for%20wearing%20for%20multiple%20hours%20if%20you're%2C%20say%2C%20walking%20around%20a%20city%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20pick%20the%20best%20walking%20shoes%20for%20women%3Ch3%3EWhat%20to%20avoid%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20most%20of%20us%20walk%20in%20whatever%20sneakers%20we%20already%20have%20on%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20categories%20of%20shoes%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Daughtry%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20wear%20walking%20more%20than%2010%20minutes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFashion%20sneakers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-sneakers-for-women%5C%22%3Estylish%20sneakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20designed%20with%20a%20more%20narrow%20toe%20box%20and%20low%20to%20no%20cushioning%20or%20support%20for%20better%20aesthetics.%20But%20the%20trade-off%20is%20zero%20shock%20absorption%20and%20more%20strain%20on%20your%20foot%20when%20walking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECertain%20r