efits%20beyond%20treating%20men%20suffering%20from%20erectile%20dysfunction%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ox.ac.uk%2Fnews%2F2024-06-07-sildenafil-viagra-improves-brain-blood-flow-and-could-help-prevent-dementia%5C%22%3Enew%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20found.%20The%20drug%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20enhance%20blood%20flow%20to%20the%20brain%20and%20improve%20the%20function%20of%20blood%20vessels%20in%20individuals%20at%20high%20risk%20of%20vascular%20dementia%2C%20says%20the%20research%20carried%20out%20by%20scientists%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnVascular%20dementia%20is%20a%20condition%20that%20majorly%20impacts%20cognitive%20functions%2C%20including%20judgement%2C%20memory%20and%20others.%20This%20happens%20due%20to%20the%20reduced%20blood%20supply%20to%20the%20brain%20affecting%20brain%20tissue%20and%20damaging%20it.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Circulation%20Research%2C%20marks%20a%20potentially%20pivotal%20step%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20dementia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EKey%20findings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnScientists%20found%20that%20Sildenafil%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20increase%20blood%20flow%20in%20both%20large%20and%20small%20brain%20vessels%2C%20which%20were%20measured%20by%20ultrasound%20and%20MRI%20scans.%20It%20enhanced%20the%20blood%20flow%20response%20to%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20indicating%20improved%20cerebrovascular%20function.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFurther%2C%20sildenafil%2C%20along%20with%20cilostazol%2C%20lowered%20blood%20vessel%20resistance%20in%20the%20brain%2C%20the%20study%20suggested.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20it%20noted%20that%20Sildenafil%20caused%20fewer%20side%20effects%20in%20comparison%20with%20cilostazol%2C%20particularly%20with%20less%20incidence%20of%20diarrhoea.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20trial%20to%20show%20that%20sildenafil%20gets%20into%20the%20blood%20vessels%20in%20the%20brain%20in%20people%20with%20this%20condition%2C%20improving%20blood%20flow%20and%20how%20responsive%20these%20blood%20vessels%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Alastair%20Webb%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20the%20Wolfson%20Centre%20for%20Prevention%20of%20Stroke%20and%20Dementia%20at%20Oxford%20University.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20asserted%20that%20these%20factors%20are%20associated%20with%20chronic%20damage%20to%20the%20small%20blood%20vessels%20inside%20the%20brain%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20causes%20of%20vascular%20dementia.%20%26quot%3BThis%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20this%20well-tolerated%2C%20widely-available%20drug%20to%20prevent%20dementia%2C%20which%20needs%20testing%20in%20larger%20trials%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Webb%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNoting%20that%20vascular%20dementia%20currently%20lacks%20specific%20therapies%2C%20the%20report%20claimed%20that%20chronic%20damage%20to%20the%20small%20blood%20vessels%20in%20the%20brain%20is%20not%20the%20only%20leading%20cause%20of%20this%20condition%2C%20as%20it%20also%20contributes%20to%2030%25%20of%20strokes%20and%2080%25%20of%20brain%20bleeds.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20OxHARP%20trial%20involved%2075%20participants%20who%20experienced%20a%20minor%20stroke%2C%20showing%20signs%20of%20mild%20to%20moderate%20small%20vessel%20disease.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEach%20participant%20was%20given%20sildenafil%2C%20a%20placebo%2C%20and%20cilostazol%20--%20a%20similar%20drug%20--%20over%20a%20three-week%20period.%20To%20evaluate%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20drugs%2C%20the%20study%20employed%20cardiovascular%20physiology%20tests%2C%20ultrasound%20as%20well%20as%20functional%20MRI%20scans.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718216460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fj8nfhrlo_viagra-generic_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fviagra-improves-brain-blood-flow-may-help-pr