icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcxee43mdd60o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcxee43mdd60o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcxee43mdd60o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20First%20Odisha%20Cabinet%20Meet%2C%20A%20Big%20Decision%20On%20Puri%20Jagannath%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOdisha's%20BJP%20government%20in%20its%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%20approved%20a%20proposal%20to%20re-open%20all%20four%20gates%20of%20Shree%20Jagannath%20Temple%20in%20Puri%20on%20early%20Thursday%20morning%20and%20set%20up%20a%20corpus%20fund%20for%20immediate%20requirement%20of%20the%2012th-century%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20stated%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%20after%20chairing%20a%20meeting%20with%20his%20ministers%20at%20the%20state%20secretariat%20Lok%20Seva%20Bhawan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20decided%20to%20re-open%20all%20the%20four%20gates%20of%20the%20Puri%20Jagannath%20temple%20in%20early%20morning%20tomorrow%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20all%20ministers.%20Devotees%20will%20have%20access%20to%20the%20temple%20through%20all%20four%20gates%2C%26quot%3B%20Majhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20opening%20all%20the%20temple%20gates%20was%20one%20of%20the%20promises%20of%20the%20BJP's%20election%20manifesto%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20devotees%20were%20facing%20problems%20due%20to%20closure%20of%20the%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20BJD%20administration%20continued%20to%20keep%20the%20four%20gates%20of%20the%20temple%20closed%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20The%20devotees%20can%20enter%20through%20only%20one%20gate%20and%20there%20were%20demands%20that%20all%20gates%20be%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20sake%20of%20conservation%20and%20preservation%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20Majhi%20said%20the%20Cabinet%20decided%20to%20constitute%20a%20corpus%20fund%20of%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20look%20after%20the%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20all%20ministers%20will%20leave%20for%20Puri%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20and%20stay%20in%20the%20pilgrim%20town%20so%20that%20they%20can%20be%20present%20when%20all%20four%20gates%20will%20be%20opened%20on%20Thursday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajhi%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20will%20also%20take%20steps%20to%20raise%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20of%20paddy%20to%20Rs%203100%20per%20quintal%20and%20the%20department%20concerned%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20take%20measures%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20committee%20will%20be%20formed%20very%20soon%20for%20implementation%20of%20the%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20MSP%20for%20paddy%20to%20Rs%203100%20per%20quintal%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20apart%2C%20a%20special%20policy%20%26quot%3BSamruddha%20Krushak%20Niti%20Yojana%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20framed%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20problems%20of%20farmers%20including%20the%20MSP%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20departments%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20prepare%20a%20proper%20guideline%20and%20roadmap%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20present%20it%20before%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20done%20within%20a%20span%20of%20first%20100%20days%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajhi%20also%20claimed%20that%20efforts%20of%20the%20previous%20BJD%20regime%20for%20women%20empowerment%20and%20child%20welfare%20have%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20new%20government%20will%20implement%20the%20Subhdra%20Yojana%20within%20100%20days%20under%20which%20the%20women%20will%20get%20a%20Rs%2050%2C000%20cash%20voucher%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20departments%20are%20told%20to%20prepare%20guidelines%20and%20roadmaps%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Subhadra%20Yojana%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718213580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fq067dafg_jagannath-temple-puri-odisha_625x300_21_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-meet-odisha-cabinet-decides-to-reopen-all-4-jagannath-temple-gates-5876834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Odisha's%20BJP%20government%20in%20its%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%20approved%20a%20proposal%20to%20re-open%20all%20four%20gates%20of%20Shree%20Jagannath%20Temple%20in%20Puri%20on%20early%20Thursday%20morning%20and%20set%20up%20a%20corpus%20fund%20for%20immediate%20requirement%20of%20the%2012th-century%20shrine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-meet-odisha-cabinet-decides-to-reopen-all-4-jagannath-temple-gates-5876834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-meet-odisha-cabinet-decides-to-reopen-all-4-jagannath-temple-gates-5876834%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-meet-odisha-cabinet-decides-to-reopen-all-4-jagannath-temple-gates-5876834%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20missile%20strike%20kills%209%20in%20Zelensky's%20hometown%20-%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718212809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ffa03%2Flive%2Ffeee5060-28d9-11ef-8c04-d9cb3ea38c14.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv22kzp0m0zo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%2029%20people%20are%20injured%20in%20the%20missile%20attack%20on%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Kryvyi%20Rih%2C%20Ukraine%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv22kzp0m0zo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv22kzp0m0zo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv22kzp0m0zo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20One%20Can%20Restrain%20Adults%20From%20Marrying%20As%20Per%20Their%20Will%3A%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20quashed%20a%20kidnapping%20case%20against%20a%20man%20registered%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20his%20wife's%20uncle%20after%20the%20couple%20eloped%20and%20said%20the%20judicial%20magistrate%20was%20wrong%20in%20sending%20the%20adult%20petitioner%20back%20to%20her%20parental%20home%20even%20when%20she%20had%20expressed%20fear%20for%20her%20life%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20can%20restrain%20an%20adult%20from%20going%20anywhere%20that%20he%20or%20she%20likes%2C%20staying%20with%20a%20person%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%2C%20or%20solemnising%20marriage%20according%20to%20his%2F%20her%20will%20or%20wish%20as%20this%20is%20a%20right%20which%20flows%20from%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20provides%20protection%20of%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20aged%20about%2021%20years%20had%20married%20the%20man%20according%20to%20Muslim%20rites%20in%20April%202024%2C%20regarding%20which%20the%20Telangana%20state%20waqf%20board%20issued%20a%20marriage%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20uncle%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20her%20husband%20under%20section%20363%20(kidnapping)%20of%20IPC.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20police%20not%20only%20arrested%20her%20husband%20but%20also%20took%20the%20woman%20into%20custody%20and%20handed%20her%20over%20to%20her%20uncle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20produced%20the%20woman%20before%20the%20Magistrate%20to%20get%20her%20statement%20recorded%20under%20Section%20164%20CrPC%2C%20she%20categorically%20said%20that%20she%20had%20married%20the%20man%20of%20her%20own%20choice%20and%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20been%20implicated%20in%20the%20case%20falsely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20couple%20jointly%20challenged%20the%20FIR%20before%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20comprising%20justices%20JJ%20Munir%20and%20Justice%20Arun%20Kumar%20Singh%20Deshwal%20said%20the%20judicial%20magistrate%20had%20sent%20the%20woman%20to%20her%20uncle's%20home%20despite%20her%20statement%20under%20section%20164%20of%20the%20criminal%20procedure%20code%20(CrPC)%2C%20wherein%20she%20had%20expressed%20fear%20for%20her%20life%20if%20sent%20to%20her%20uncle%2Fparent's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20the%20judicial%20magistrate%2C%20before%20whom%20the%20first%20petitioner%20lady%20claimed%20that%20she%20feared%20for%20her%20life%20because%20her%20uncle%20had%20threatened%20to%20do%20her%20death%2C%20was%20duty%20bound%20to%20get%20an%20FIR%20registered%20against%20the%20uncle%2C%20besides%20taking%20adequate%20measures%20to%20secure%20the%20safety%20and%20life%20of%20the%20first%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20the%20honour%20killing%20in%20such%20matters%20is%20not%20an%20unknown%20phenomenon%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20added%20that%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Siddharth%20Nagar%20and%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%2C%20police%20station-Bansi%2C%20Siddharth%20Nagar%20district%20were%20equally%20answerable%20for%20not%20taking%20action%20against%20the%20woman's%20uncle%20by%20registering%20an%20appropriate%20FIR%20and%20safeguarding%20the%20woman's%20life%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20the%20above%20observations%2C%20the%20court%20quashed%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20decision%20dated%20June%207%2C%20the%20court%20also%20directed%20the%20officers%20concerned%20to%20ensure%20that%20her%20uncle%20or%20any%20other%20family%20member%20does%20not%20harm%20her%20in%20any%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718212560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmpbrq8a_allahabad-high-court_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-one-can-restrain-adults-from-marrying-as-per-their-will-allahabad-high-court-5876897%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20quashed%20a%20kidnapping%20case%20against%20a%20man%20registered%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20his%20wife's%20uncle%20after%20the%20couple%20eloped%20and%20said%20the%20judicial%20magistrate%20was%20wrong%20in%20sending%20the%20adult%20petitioner%20back%20to%20her%20parental%20home%20even%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-one-can-restrain-adults-from-marrying-as-per-their-will-allahabad-high-court-5876897%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-one-can-restrain-adults-from-marrying-as-per-their-will-allahabad-high-court-5876897%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-one-can-restrain-adults-from-marrying-as-per-their-will-allahabad-high-court-5876897%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Crisis%20In%20Delhi%2C%20Tankers%20Stealing%20Water%20From%20Canal%2C%20NDTV%20Finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20crisis%20in%20Delhi%20has%20blown%20up%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20political%20controversy%2C%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20being%20accused%20of%20being%20unable%20to%20stop%20water%20theft%20from%20the%20Munak%20canal.%20The%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20water%20mafia%20is%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20Officials%20of%20Raj%20Niwas%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20house%2C%20have%20also%20blamed%20the%20AAP%20government%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20water%20mafia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20water%20mafia%20is%20stealing%20water%20in%20collusion%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20officials%20and%20has%20complained%20about%20it%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%20AAP%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20Haryana%20is%20not%20releasing%20the%20water%C2%A0%20it%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20give%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20reporting%20from%20Ground%20Zero%20spotted%20tanker%20pumping%20water%20illegally%20from%20the%20Delhi-Haryana%20Munak%20canal%2C%20which%20is%20practically%20the%20sole%20supplier%20of%20water%20for%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20highlighted%20the%20dwindling%20numbers%20of%20water%20tankers%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20January%202023%2C%201179%20tankers%20were%20deployed%20by%20DJB%2C%20and%20in%20June%202023%2C%20this%20number%20was%201203.%20However%2C%20this%20number%20was%20reduced%20to%20888%20in%20January%202024%2C%20without%20any%20approval%20from%20me%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20without%20any%20consultation%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claimed%20her%20repeated%20requests%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20tankers%20were%20ignored%20by%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20DJB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20declared%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Btanker%20mafia%20has%20strengthened%20in%20Delhi%26quot%3B%20since%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20came%20to%20power%20and%20they%20have%20submitted%20evidence%20of%20this%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saxena%20has%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20chief%20to%20maintain%20strict%20vigil%20along%20the%20Munak%20canal%20to%20prevent%20any%20further%20theft%20of%20water.%20Wrongdoers%20should%20be%20arrested%20and%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20them.%20A%20compliance%20report%20should%20be%20filed%20within%20a%20week%2C%20he%20has%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20questioned%20what%20action%20the%20Delhi%20government%20is%20taking%20about%20tank%20mafias%20and%20how%20it%20is%20planning%20to%20ensure%20water%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20needs%201%2C300%20million%20gallons%20per%20day%2C%20or%20MGD%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Delhi%20Jal%20board%20produces%20only%20an%20estimated%201%2C000%20MGD%2C%20say%20conservative%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718212320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fe2d10u5g_djb-tanker_625x300_12_June_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-water-crisis-tankers-illegally-taking-water-from-canal-ndtv-finds-5876784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20water%20crisis%20in%20Delhi%20has%20blown%20up%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20political%20controversy%2C%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20being%20accused%20of%20being%20unable%20to%20stop%20water%20theft%20from%20the%20Munak%20canal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-water-crisis-tankers-illegally-taking-water-from-canal-ndtv-finds-5876784%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-water-crisis-tankers-illegally-taking-water-from-canal-ndtv-finds-5876784%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-water-crisis-tankers-illegally-taking-water-from-canal-ndtv-finds-5876784%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C