%20hospitals.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20multi-modal%20transport%20facility%20that%20brings%20all%20plans%20to%20converge%20at%20one%20rail%20and%20road%20location%20is%20being%20planned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20eligible%20business%20in%20the%20redeveloped%20Dharavi%2C%20the%20DRPPL%20said%2C%20will%20benefit%20from%20a%20five-year%20reimbursement%20of%20the%20State%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(SGST)%20to%20foster%20economic%20growth%20and%20support%20local%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegrettably%2C%20the%20redevelopment%20project%20has%20encountered%20challenges%2C%20particularly%20from%20certain%20vested%20political%20interests%20who%20have%20interrupted%20the%20necessary%20survey%20work%20in%20various%20areas.%20While%20many%20local%20residents%20support%20the%20survey%20process%2C%20these%20disruptions%20by%20a%20few%2C%20driven%20by%20their%20own%20interests%2C%20have%20prevented%20many%20from%20moving%20into%20ready-to-occupy%20homes%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20endure%20unnecessary%20hardship%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDRPPL%20believes%20that%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20Dharavi%20should%20not%20be%20politicized%20but%20viewed%20as%20a%20collective%20effort%20for%20the%20common%20good%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20country.%20The%20project%20represents%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20a%20brighter%20future%20for%20Dharavi%2C%20Nav%20Dharavi%2C%20and%20its%20residents%2C%20aiming%20to%20transform%20the%20areas%20into%20a%20modern%20and%20thriving%20urban%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRPPL%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20engaging%20with%20the%20community%2C%20addressing%20concerns%20and%20ensuring%20transparency%20at%20every%20level%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20create%20a%20Dharavi%20and%20Nav%20Dharavi%20that%20stand%20out%20as%20a%20model%20for%20urban%20redevelopment%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3