0was%20committed%2C%20for%20a%20spot%20inspection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%2033-year-old%20Renukaswamy%20drew%20the%20wrath%20of%20Darshan%20for%20making%20lewd%20comments%20against%20Ms%20Gowda%20on%20her%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Pavithra%20who%20instigated%20Darshan%20to%20punish%20Renukaswamy.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20plan%20was%20hatched%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20claimed.%20%26quot%3BDarshan%20engaged%20the%20Chitradurga%20unit%20of%20Darshan%20Fan%20Club%20Convenor%20Raghavendra%20alias%20Raghu%2C%20who%20obtained%20all%20information%20about%20Renukaswamy.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnRenukaswamy's%20wife%20Sahana%20alleged%20that%20Raghavendra%20picked%20up%20her%20husband%20on%20Friday%20night%20from%20near%20their%20house%20in%20Chitradurga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20was%20kidnapped%20and%20taken%20to%20a%20shed%20in%20Kamakshipalya%20area%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDarshan%20beat%20up%20Renukaswamy%20with%20a%20belt.%20After%20he%20fell%20unconscious%2C%20his%20accomplices%20thrashed%20him%20with%20sticks.%20Further%2C%20they%20threw%20him%20against%20a%20wall%2C%20which%20proved%20fatal%2C%20as%20he%20suffered%20multiple%20bone%20fractures%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20after%20the%20killing%2C%20his%20body%20was%20dumped%20in%20a%20storm-water%20drain%20in%20Kamakshipalya%20area%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20food%20delivery%20boy%20who%20noticed%20stray%20dogs%20eating%20a%20human%20body%20alerted%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20were%20pursuing%20the%20case%2C%20two%20accused%20approached%20Kamakshipalya%20police%20and%20%26quot%3Bconfessed%26quot%3B%20to%20having%20killed%20Renukaswamy%20over%20a%20financial%20dispute.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20investigation%20progressed%2C%20police%20found%20out%20Darshan%20and%20Pavithra's%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%20police%20have%20been%20given%20a%20free%20hand%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%20against%20Darshan%20and%20his%20associates%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20police%20will%20probe%20and%20decide%20whether%20Darshan%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhabitual%20offender%2C%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20will%20accordingly%20invoke%20legal%20sections%20and%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Darshan%20was%20arrested%20by%20police%20for%20allegedly%20assaulting%20his%20wife%20and%20threatening%20her.%20He%20was%20later%20released%20on%20bail%20and%20the%20couple%20subsequently%20resolved%20the%20issue%20and%20she%20withdrew%20the%20case%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Film%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20(KFCC)%20President%20N%20M%20Suresh%20said%20that%20a%20decision%20regarding%20taking%20action%20against%20Darshan%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20discussion%20with%20the%20artists'%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20indicated%20that%20action%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20taken%20only%20after%20the%20police%20file%20a%20charge-sheet%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20was%20responding%20to%20members%20of%20some%20pro-Kannada%20organisations%2C%20who%20met%20him%2C%20demanding%20that%20KFCC%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20Darshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20made%20his%20debut%20as%20a%20lead%20actor%20in%20the%20movie%20'Majestic'%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20featured%20in%20several%20commercially%20successful%20films%20including%20'Kariya'%2C%20'Krantiveera%20Sangolli%20Rayanna'%2C%20'Kalasipalya'%2C%20'Gaja'%2C%20'Navagraha'%2C%20'Saarathi'%2C%20'Bulbul'%2C%20'Yajamana'%2C%20'Robert'%20and%20'Kaatera'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3