e%20IPL%20has%20increased%20by%206.3%25%20to%20US%243.4%20billion%20(INR%2028%2C000%20crores)%2C%20over%20the%20past%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20title%20sponsorship%20for%20the%20IPL%20has%20been%20secured%20by%20the%20Tata%20Group%20for%20a%20further%20five-year%20period%2C%20from%202024%20until%202028%2C%20for%20approximately%20US%24300%20million%20(INR%202%2C500%20crores)%2C%20paying%20approximately%2050%25%20more%20than%20the%20previous%20deal%20of%20INR%20335%20crores%20per%20season.%20This%2C%20along%20with%20last%20year's%20media%20rights%20auction%2C%20reinforces%20the%20IPL's%20status%20as%20a%20pivotal%20platform%20for%20esteemed%20brands%20seeking%20to%20enhance%20their%20value.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Report%20added%20that%20the%20most%20valued%20IPL%20franchise%20is%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20valuation%2C%20despite%20failing%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20playoffs%20in%202024%2C%20with%20a%20brand%20value%20of%20US%24231.0%20million%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20most%20valued%20franchisee%2C%20achieving%20a%20growth%20of%209%25%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20IPL%202024%20winners%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%2C%20saw%20the%20highest%20growth%2C%20with%20a%2019.30%25%20rise%20from%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive-time%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20are%20not%20even%20in%20the%20top%20three%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20brand%20value%2C%20the%20report%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRanked%20second%20in%20brand%20and%20business%20value%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20boasts%20a%3Cbr%3E%5Cnstaggering%20brand%20worth%20of%20US%24227.0%20million.%20Winners%20of%20the%20TATA%20IPL%202024%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20has%20replaced%20Mumbai%20Indians%20to%20secure%20the%20third%20place%20in%20brand%20value%20with%20US%24216.0%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%2C%20which%20is%20another%20immensely%20successful%20and%20popular%20team%2C%20closely%20trails%20in%20fourth%20place%20on%20the%20table%20with%20a%20brand%20value%20of%20US%24204.0%20million.%20With%20the%20return%20of%20its%20legacy%20player%20and%20new%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MI%20has%20solidified%20its%20status%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20evolving%20franchisees%20in%20IPL%20history%2C%20paving%20a%20path%20to%20player%20trades%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718196540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpnjs8nk_ipl-trophy-bcci_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frs-135-000-crore-report-claims-ipls-business-value-says-mi-not-most-valued-team-it-is-5874786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IPL%202024%20Brand%20Value%3A%20IPL%2C%20overall%20as%20an%20entity%2C%20has%20grown%20manifold%20financially%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frs-135-000-crore-report-claims-ipls-business-value-says-mi-not-most-valued-team-it-is-5874786%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frs-135-000-crore-report-claims-ipls-business-value-says-mi-not-most-valued-team-it-is-5874786%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frs-135-000-crore-report-claims-ipls-business-value-says-mi-not-most-valued-team-it-is-5874786%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohan%20Majhi%20Takes%20Oath%20As%20BJP's%20First%20Chief%20Minister%20In%20Odisha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMohan%20Charan%20Majhi%20--%20the%20first%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20Odisha%20--%20took%20oath%20with%20his%20two%20deputies%2C%20KV%20Singh%20Deo%20and%20Pravati%20Parida%2C%20this%20evening%20in%20a%20grand%20ceremony%20that%20announced%20the%20party's%20arrival%20in%20eastern%20India.%20The%20event%20is%20being%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20a%20number%20of%20Union%20ministers%20and%20other%20dignitaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20attending%20the%20event%20in%20a%20gesture%20of%20old-world%20political%20courtesy%20is%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20chief%20who%20headed%20the%20state%20for%2024%20years.%20Mr%20Majhi%20had%20driven%20to%20his%20residence%20last%20evening%20and%20invited%20him%20for%20today's%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Odisha%20changed%20its%20mandate%20this%20time%2C%20giving%20the%20BJP%2078%20of%20the%20147%20assembly%20seats.%20The%20BJD%20won%2051%20seats%2C%20and%20failed%20to%20open%20account%20in%20parliament.%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20closest%20aide%2C%20VK%20Pandiyan%2C%20who%20allegedly%20had%20a%20huge%20influence%20on%20him%2C%20quit%20the%20party%20shortly%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Majhi%2C%2052%2C%20a%20four-time%20MLA%20from%20Keonjhar%20and%20the%20party's%20tribal%20face%2C%20is%20an%20experienced%20politician%20and%20his%20public%20service%20and%20organisational%20skills%20worked%20in%20his%20favour%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20top%20post%2C%20sources%20have%20indicated.%20The%20chief%20whip%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20previous%20assembly%2C%20he%20was%20the%20youngest%20of%20the%20front-runners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20deputy%2C%20Mr%20Deo%2C%20is%20a%20six-time%20MLA%20and%20an%20erstwhile%20royal%20from%20Patna%20(princely%20state)%2C%20Bolangir%2C%20and%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20government%20for%20nine%20years%20till%202009%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20were%20in%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPravati%20Parida%2C%2057%2C%20a%20first-time%20MLA%2C%20has%20been%20in%20the%20party%20for%20the%20last%2028%20years.%20She%20was%20chief%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20women's%20wing%20(2016-2022)%20and%20the%20state%20BJP%20Vice%20President%20(2022-2024).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha's%20change%20of%20heart%20came%20after%20a%20proposed%20alliance%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20BJD%20fell%20through.%20The%C2%A0%20BJP%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20tough%20campaign%2C%20focussing%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20development%20in%20many%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20allegations%20the%20BJD%20stoutly%20denied.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20alienated%20the%20voters%20were%20the%20local-level%20instances%20of%20corruption%20that%20flourished%20despite%20the%20clean%20image%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20There%20were%20allegations%20that%20the%20local%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJD%20sought%20bribes%20to%20ensure%20provision%20of%20government%20services.%20Ensconced%20at%20his%20residence%20post-Covid%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20uncaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20break%20into%20the%20eastern%20India%2C%20after%20its%20successful%C2%A0%20venture%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20had%20stepped%20into%20the%20breach%2C%20promising%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20new%20generation%20and%20appealing%20to%20the%20Odiya%20asmita.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718196300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm3stoai_manoj-majhi_625x300_12_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohan-majhi-takes-oath-as-bjps-first-chief-minister-in-odisha-5874646%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%20--%20the%20first%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20Odisha%20--%20took%20oath%20with%20his%20two%20deputies%2C%20KV%20Singh%20Deo%20and%20Pravati%20Parida%2C%20this%20evening%20in%20a%20grand%20ceremony%20that%20announced%20the%20party's%20arrival%20in%20eastern%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%