'service'%20to%20several%20other%20people%20through%20a%20network%20of%20brokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ajay%20Tawade%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Sassoon%20Hospital's%20Forensic%20Medical%20Department%2C%20who%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20and%20is%20in%20judicial%20custody%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20who%20had%20allegedly%20switched%20the%20minor's%20blood%20samples%20with%20those%20of%20his%20mother%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20alcohol%20was%20found%20in%20the%20final%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20Pune%20Crime%20Branch%20told%20NDTV%20that%20their%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20that%20this%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Dr%20Tawade%20had%20done%20something%20like%20that.%20Whenever%20there%20were%20high-profile%20cases%20of%20drunk%20drivers%20running%20over%20and%20killing%20people%2C%20the%20doctor's%20brokers%2C%20spread%20across%20Pune%20and%20four%20other%20districts%20in%20Western%20Maharashtra%2C%20would%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20families%20and%20offer%20to%20switch%20their%20blood%20samples%20with%20clean%20ones%20so%20that%20the%20accused%20could%20get%20away%20with%20a%20milder%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20brokers%20would%20demand%20lakhs%20for%20the%20service%2C%20usually%20above%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20and%20the%20money%20would%20be%20funnelled%20to%20Dr%20Tawade%2C%20with%20them%20keeping%20a%20cut%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20had%20been%20going%20on%20since%20the%20doctor%20took%20over%20the%20forensic%20department%20nearly%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tawade%20has%20faced%20serious%20allegations%20earlier%20as%20well.%20He%20had%20been%20accused%20in%20drug%20cases%20and%20a%20kidney%20transplant%20racket%2C%20and%20had%20allegedly%20been%20elevated%20to%20the%20post%20of%20the%20forensic%20department%20head%20at%20the%20recommendation%20of%20an%20MLA%20and%20a%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Vin