nd-bob-dylan-dies-13151833%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrancoise-hardy-french-music-icon-who-inspired-sir-mick-jagger-and-bob-dylan-dies-13151833%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trouble%20For%20India%3F%20Dravid%20Speaks%20To%20Off-Colour%20Star.%20Insider%20With%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20bowling%20coach%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20has%20backed%20'vastly%20experienced'%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20come%20good%20in%20the%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20left-arm%20spin%20all-rounder%20will%20be%20winning%20matches%20for%20the%20team%20later%20in%20the%20competition.%20In%20the%20ongoing%20tournament%2C%20Jadeja%20is%20yet%20to%20pick%20a%20wicket%20with%20the%20ball%20and%20was%20dismissed%20for%20a%20golden%20duck%20by%20Mohammed%20Amir%20in%20India's%20thrilling%20six-run%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20at%20New%20York%20on%20June%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Axar%20chipping%20in%20with%20valuable%20all-round%20contributions%20in%20India's%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20and%20in-form%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kuldeep%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63624-kuldeep-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20waiting%20in%20the%20ranks%20to%20be%20in%20the%20playing%20eleven%2C%20Jadeja%20is%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20in%20terms%20of%20his%20position%20in%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20team%20game%2C%20right%3F%20It's%20going%20to%20be%2011%20guys.%20You%20really%20don't%20expect%20all%20of%20them%20coming%20into%20form.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20performed%20every%20game%20that%20will%20happen.%20For%20me%2C%20I%20personally%20feel%20whatever%20conversations%20Rahul%20(Dravid%2C%20head%20coach)%20and%20Vicky%20(Vikram%20Rathour%2C%20batting%20coach)%20are%20having%20around%2C%20I've%20been%20pretty%20happy%20with%20it.%20You%20expect%20a%20one-odd%20game%20out%20there.%20But%20it's%20a%20long%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20someone%20like%20Jadeja%2C%20who's%20so%20vastly%20experienced%2C%20he%20just%20needs%20a%20game%20out%20there%20to%20just%20get%20his%20root%20and%20feel%20around.%20We%20know%20that%20the%20skills%20and%20experience%20he%20has%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20win%20you%20games.%20So%20that%20confidence%20we%20have%20in%20not%20only%20Jadeja%2C%20but%20honestly%20with%20someone%20like%20(Shivam)%20Dube%20and%20others%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20one%20odd%20game%20and%20people%20will%20have%20conversations%20saying%20you%20are%20being%20given%20a%20game%2C%20and%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20that%20one%20bad%20game.%20That's%20fine%2C%20but%20the%20team%20will%20back%20you%20and%20that's%20what%20is%20important%20in%20a%20tournament%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mhambrey%20ahead%20of%20India's%20clash%20against%20USA%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Kuldeep%20yet%20to%20get%20a%20game%20in%20the%20tournament%20due%20to%20seam-friendly%20nature%20of%20New%20York%20drop-in%20pitches%2C%20Mhambrey%20said%20the%20left-arm%20wrist%20spinner%20understands%20that%20him%20being%20not%20in%20the%20playing%20eleven%20is%20down%20to%20team%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20opponents%20and%20surface.%20With%20Axar%20also%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20IPL%2C%20he's%20bowled%20very%20well.%20I%20think%20that's%20an%20advantage%20that%20we%20have%20out%20here%20for%20us.%20In%20terms%20of%20the%20performance%20and%20the%20rhythm%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20confidence%2C%20he's%20up%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDropping%20a%20seamer%20and%20playing%20a%20spinner%20(does%20happen%20by)%20looking%20at%20the%20conditions%2C%20but%20also%20the%20other%20thing%20that%20Axar%20does%20is%2C%20he%20gives%20you%20that%20depth%20as%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20batting%2C%20which%20was%20pretty%20evident%20in%20the%20last%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20had%20to%20promote%20someone%20like%20him%2C%20we%20had%20to%20take%20a%20chance.%20He%20played%20a%20very%20critical%20role%20for%20the%20team%2C%20got%20those%20runs%20at%20that%20stage%2C%20because%20the%20ball%20was%20challenging%20at%20that%20situation%20%E2%80%93%20seaming%20and%20swinging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20India%20will%20always%20have%20their%20number%20eight%20position%20based%20on%20the%20batting%20returns%2C%20Mhambrey%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20so.%20I%20think%20it's%20(the)%20surface.%20It's%20purely%20on%20the%20opponents%2C%20purely%20on%20the%20surface.%20If%20you%20feel%2C%20maybe%20on%20a%20surface%2C%20you%20need%20one%20extra%20bowler.%20We%20will%20go%20with%20that%20combination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMhambrey%20has%20also%20been%20pleased%20with%20the%20pitches%20becoming%20better%20to%20play%20on%20now%20at%20the%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium.%20%26quot%3BThe%20pitches%20have%20looked%20a%20bit%20better%20now%2C%20but%20the%20first%201-2%20games%2C%20there%20was%20odd%20bounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20batter%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20go%20through%20with%20your%20shots%20when%20that%20happens.%20Sure%2C%20it's%20challenging%2C%20but%20the%20bowlers%20are%20finally%20getting%20some%20help%20and%20that's%20good%20too.%20We%20saw%20what%20happened%20during%20the%20IPL%2C%20big%2C%20big%20scores%2C%20so%20this%20sort%20of%20evens%20it%20out%20a%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bowling%20coach%20signed%20off%20by%20lavishing%20praise%20on%20USA%20left-arm%20fast-bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Saurabh%20Netravalkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F121208-saurabh-netravalkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESaurabh