024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20aims%20to%20accommodate%203.52%20million%20passengers%20by%202025-2026.%20The%20new%20terminal%20is%20a%20two-storeyed%20building%20with%20a%20built-up%20area%20of%2075%2C000%20square%20metres.%C2%A0has%2060%20check-in%20desks%2C%205%20baggage%20carousels%20and%20advanced%20security%20systems.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20airport%20can%20now%20handle%203%2C500%20international%20passengers%20during%20peak%20hours%20and%20more%20than%204.5%20million%20passengers%20annually%2C%20up%20from%201.5%20million%20previously.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20terminal%20includes%20energy-efficient%20canopies%2C%20LED%20lighting%20and%20a%20solar%20power%20plant.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20also%20features%20a%20new%20apron%2C%20the%20area%20where%20aircraft%20are%20parked%2C%20loaded%20or%20unloaded%2C%20refuelled%2C%20and%20boarded%2C%20along%20with%20an%20air%20traffic%20control%20tower%20and%20other%20airside%20facilities.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20multi-level%20car%20parking%20space%20for%20750%20cars%2C%20250%20taxis%20and%2010%20buses.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20expansion%20project%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20through%20AAI%2C%20with%20a%20total%20investment%20of%20%E2%82%B9%209.51%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718191320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6gvllji8_tiruchi-airport-_625x300_12_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanand-mahindra-shares-pictures-of-tiruchirapalli-airport-terminal-lauds-design-elements-5874401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mahindra%20Chairperson%20said%20that%20the%20new%20terminal%20%26quot%3Blooks%20wonderful%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20emphasis%20on%20local%20culture%20%26amp%3B%20design%20elements.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanand-mahindra-shares-pictures-of-tiruchirapalli-airport-terminal-la