2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20highlights%20how%20the%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Efarsan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(snack)%20shop%20idea%20that%20that%20family%20had%20started.%20And%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20outlet%20is%20none%20other%20than%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20himself%2C%20who%20recommended%20the%20place%20to%20a%20contestant%20on%20the%20sets%20of%20the%20reality%20game%20show%20%E2%80%98Kaun%20Banega%20Crorepati%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Shivaji%20Park%20Vada%20Pav%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F243528%2Fmumbai-best-vada-pav-stall-food-origin-ashok-vaidya-maharashtra-history-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20garlic%3Cem%3E%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20create%20a%20beautiful%20symphony.%20The%20duo%20has%20found%20favour%20in%20Sachin%20Tendulkar.%20As%20he%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3ECurly%20Tales%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20his%20growing-up%20years.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20hours%20of%20practising%20on%20the%20field%2C%20I%20used%20to%20have%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20canteen%20and%20would%20eat%20four%20to%20five%20of%20them%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20years%20haven%E2%80%99t%20diminished%20the%20love%20it%20seems.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20Marathi%20portal%20in%202011%2C%20Tendulkar%20reiterated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20and%20my%20son%20(Arjun)%20love%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Evada-pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%20Gymkhana%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20that%20can%20beat%20this%20snack%2C%20laced%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Swati%20Snacks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20belly%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Tardeo%20lies%20an%20eatery%20that%20has%20stuck%20to%20one%20philosophy%3A%20home%20food%20is%20the%20best%20food.%20Minakshi%20Jhaveri%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252694%2Fswati-snacks-minakshi-jhaveri-iconic-eatery-india-inspiring-single-mother-success-stories-authentic-homemade-food-chaat-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwati%20Snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20any%20prior%20business%20acumen%2C%20serving%20four%20items%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Esev%20puri%2C%20bhel%20puri%2C%20ragda%20pattice%20and%20pani%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20priced%20at%20four%20%3Cem%3Eaanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20currency%20unit%20used%20in%20British%20India).%20But%20with%20this%20simple%20formula%2C%20she%20created%20history%20and%20a%20multi-crore%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20Anand%20once%20shared%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20treated%20all%20her%20customers%20the%20way%20she%20would%20guests%20who%20visit%20our%20home.%20For%20a%20guest%2C%20who%20is%20equivalent%20to%20God%2C%20you%20will%20prepare%20the%20food%20with%20the%20best%20intentions%20and%20a%20positive%20attitude%2C%20which%20automatically%20reflects%20in%20the%20taste.%20While%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20watched%20her%20spend%20that%20extra%20hour%20just%20so%20she%20could%20inspect%20the%20ingredients%20multiple%20times%2C%20or%20even%20walk%20kilometres%20to%20procure%20fresh%20ingredients%20like%20coriander.%20That%20dedication%20and%20care%20is%20what%20we%20have%20inherited%20from%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThanks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMadhuriDixit%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40madhuridixit%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20introducing%20me%20to%20my%20very%20first%20Vada%20Pav%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20delicious!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTh40jqAEGa%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTh40jqAEGa%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Tim%20Cook%20(%40tim_cook)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftim_cook%2Fstatus%2F1647969544437399554%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20has%20seen%20the%20likes%20of%20legendary%20painter%20M%20F%20Husain%20and%20%3Cem%3Etabla%3C%2Fem%3E%20maestro%20Zakir%20Hussain.%20In%20a%202020%20article%20by%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Michelin%20star%20chef%20Ravinder%20Bhogal%20of%20Jikoni%20in%20London%20hailed%20the%20eatery%20for%20its%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20addition%20to%20this%20list%20was%20Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20who%20snacked%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20along%20with%20actress%20Madhuri%20Dixit%20while%20on%20his%20visit%20to%20Mumbai%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Jai%20Maharashtra%20Vadapav%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fchef.saransh%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0N149N6gQ3eiHBExBBaaNeQtuUcRASDJ7yRNKSYcy9RrrGkPngVquyB6xqZP2LUPEl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%26is_preview%3Dtrue%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Andheri%20West%2C%20the%20eatery%20serves%20no-nonsense%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20manages%20to%20hit%20it%20off%20with%20one%E2%80%99s%20taste%20buds%20almost%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20celebrity%20chef%20Saransh%20Goila%20took%20to%20Facebook%20to%20share%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20vada%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20seasoned%20perfectly%20with%20lots%20of%20coriander%20in%20it%20and%20is%20really%20crisp%20on%20the%20outside%20with%20a%20thick%20%3Cem%3Ebesan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20flour)%20coating%2C%20I%20suspect%20some%20rice%20flour%20in%20the%20batter!%20The%20%3Cem%3Epudina%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mint-flavoured%20sauce)%20consistency%20kinda%20%3Cem%3Ethecha%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20real%20star%20and%20adds%20a%20lovely%20kick%2C%20also%20the%20garlic%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20on%20point.%20I%20gobbled%20down%20three%20of%20these%20and%20yet%20I%20want%20one%20more.%20Probably%20the%20best%20lunch%20you%20can%20buy%20in%20Rs%2015!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717494416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FClassic-Vada-Pav-1-1716555449.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Vada%20pav'%2C%20the%20beloved%20Indian%20snack%2C%20never%20fails%20to%20evoke%20nostalgia%20and%20emotional%20connections.%20Mumbai%20boasts%20iconic%20spots%20like%20Aram%2C%20Ashok%20Vaidya%20Vada%20Pav%2C%20Swati%20Snacks%2C%20and%20more%2C%20each%20offering%20unique%20renditions%20of%20this%20culinary%20classic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351102%2Fbest-vada-pav-places-mumbai-ashok-vaidya-aram-shankar-gajanan-swati-snacks-jai-maharashtra-shivaji-park%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Use%20Cardboard%20Boxes%20to%20Protect%20Your%20Plants%20From%20The%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20you%20receive%20a%20package%2C%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20the%20cardboard%20waste%3F%20In%20India%2C%20households%2C%20itinerant%20waste%20merchants%2C%20and%20garbage%20collectors%20jointly%20recover%202.4%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0921344915300082%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHouseholds%252C%2520itinerant%2520waste%2520merchants%2520and%2Ctonnes%2520of%2520plastic%252C%2520more%2520than1.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4.3%20million%20tonnes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20cardboard%20and%20mixed%20paper%20annually.%20Overall%2C%2030%E2%80%9360%20percent%20of%20all%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20is%20recycled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata-based%20Krishna%20Khuku%20has%20found%20an%20innovative%20way%20to%20transform%20used%20delivery%20boxes%20into%20plant%20protectors.%20She%20shares%20three%20possible%20and%20easy%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20As%20a%20protective%20layer%20against%20heat%20waves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20says%20cardboard%20protects%20plants%20from%20heat%20waves%20while%20keeping%20the%20soil%20moist%20and%20preventing%20pest%20attacks.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F186864%2Fmumbai-girl-recycles-waste-organic-compost-raises-lakhs-dharavi-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUsing%20cardboard%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereduces%20evaporation%20from%20the%20top%20exposed%20soil%2C%20preventing%20it%20from%20drying%20out%20by%20holding%20the%20moisture%20in.%20It%20promotes%20more%20steady%20soil%20temperature%20overall.%20It%20will%20suppress%20weed%20growth%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20As%20a%20mulch%20to%20nourish%20soil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20says%20using%20cardboard%20as%20mulch%20nourishes%20the%20soil%20while%20it%E2%80%99s%20decomposing.%20She%20also%20advises%20using%20cardboards%20that%20are%20100%20percent%20recyclable%20or%20compostable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20As%20a%20filling%20for%20large%20grow%20bags%20for%20composting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20says%20filling%20grow%20bags%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278855%2Furban-garden-homemaker-grow-vegetable-fruits-flowers-organ